./.body:
1. Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle1.1. Features Overview1. Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle
1.1. Features Overview
Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle provides the interface package for the communication between panel and Tuya Cloud to accelerate the application development process
Supported hardware device type: WIFI 
Unsupported hardware device types: Zigbee、Mesh、BLE
Supported Features：Device panel control and alarm
Unsupported Feature：Groups panel control
Documentation has been migrated to BizBundle Doc

resource/Preparation.html.title: Preparation for integration
resource/Preparation.html.body:
1. Preparation for Integration1. Preparation for Integration
Tuya Smart Android Device Control Biz Bundle relies on the Tuya Smart Home Android SDK. Before starting to develop with the SDK, you need to register a developer account, create a product, etc. on the Tuya Smart Development Platform, and obtain a key to activate the SDK, please refer to Tuya Smart Home Android SDK Preparation work.
